Appendix E: Training Algorithms

E.1 Full Training Procedure (Pseudocode)

```
Algorithm 1: UMVIS Training

Input: Dataset D of (speech, text, speaker_id, emotion_prompt) tuples
       Hyperparameters: batch_size, learning_rate, total_steps
Output: Trained model parameters θ, φ, ψ

Initialize model parameters θ (encoders, SSM, decoders)
Initialize variational parameters φ
Initialize CLUB network parameters ψ
Initialize VAMPrior pseudo-inputs U

for step = 1 to total_steps:
    Sample batch {(x_i, y_i, s_i, e_i)}_{i=1}^B from D
    
    # Forward pass
    z_c, z_p, z_s, z_eps = EncodeAndFactorize(x_i, y_i, s_i, e_i)
    
    # SSM dynamics
    for t = 1 to T:
        u_t = GetInputAtTime(t, x_i, y_i)
        z_t = SSM_Step(z_{t-1}, u_t)
        Store z_t
    
    # Decode
    y_hat = TextDecoder(z_c)
    x_hat = SpeechDecoder(z)
    
    # Predict future latent (for predictive head)
    tau = RandomChoice([200, 300, 400, 500])  # ms
    t_pred = RandomSample(1, T - tau_to_frames(tau))
    z_future_hat = Predictor(z[t_pred], partial_transcript_up_to(t_pred))
    
    # Compute losses
    L_text = CTC_Loss(y_i, y_hat)
    L_speech = MultiDomainReconstructionLoss(x_i, x_hat)
    L_align = SoftDTW(z_c, TextEmbeddings(y_i)) + InfoNCE(z_c, TextEmbeddings(y_i))
    L_prosody = ProsodySupervisionLoss(extract_prosody(x_i), z_p)
    L_cmi = ConditionalCLUB(z_p, z_s, z_c, ψ)
    L_orth = OrthogonalityPenalty(z_c, z_p, z_s)
    L_anchor = AnchorSynchronizationLoss(z_c, z_p, phoneme_boundaries)
    L_contract = ContractivePenalty(A_bar)
    L_predict = MSE(z[t_pred+tau_frames], z_future_hat)
    
    L_total = α1*L_text + α2*L_speech + α3*L_align + α4*L_prosody 
            + α5*L_cmi + α6*L_orth + α7*L_anchor + α8*L_contract + α9*L_predict
    
    # Backward pass
    L_total.backward()
    ClipGradients(max_norm=1.0)
    optimizer.step()
    optimizer.zero_grad()
    
    # Update CLUB network separately (maximize its likelihood)
    L_club_update = -LogLikelihood(z_s | z_p, z_c; ψ)
    L_club_update.backward()
    club_optimizer.step()
    club_optimizer.zero_grad()
    
    # Periodic update of VAMPrior pseudo-inputs
    if step % 1000 == 0:
        UpdatePseudoInputs(U, recent_batch_samples)
```

E.2 Masked Prosody Model (MPM) Pretraining

```
Algorithm 2: MPM Pretraining

Input: Unlabeled speech dataset D_speech
Output: Pretrained speech encoder and prosody extractor

Initialize speech encoder E and prosody decoder D

for step = 1 to pretrain_steps:
    Sample speech segment x of length L (e.g., 10 seconds)
    
    # Extract features
    h = E(x)  # frame-level features
    
    # Mask random spans
    mask = GenerateRandomSpans(L, span_length=100-300ms, mask_prob=0.15)
    h_masked = h * (1 - mask)
    
    # Extract ground truth prosody features
    F0_gt = CREPE(x)
    energy_gt = RMS(x)
    
    # Predict prosody from masked features
    F0_pred, energy_pred = D(h_masked)
    
    # Loss on masked positions only
    L_mpm = MSE(F0_gt[mask], F0_pred[mask]) + MSE(energy_gt[mask], energy_pred[mask])
    
    L_mpm.backward()
    optimizer.step()
```

E.3 Anchor Synchronization Loss Computation

```
Algorithm 3: Anchor Loss with Forced Alignment

Input: Content latent z_c [T_c, d_c], Prosody latent z_p [T_p, d_p]
       Phoneme boundaries B = {b_1, b_2, ..., b_K} (in frames)
Output: Anchor loss value

# Interpolate latents to common temporal resolution if needed
z_c_interp = InterpolateToTargetFrames(z_c, target_frames=T_target)
z_p_interp = InterpolateToTargetFrames(z_p, target_frames=T_target)

# Project to shared space
z_c_proj = MLP_c(z_c_interp)  # [T_target, d_shared]
z_p_proj = MLP_p(z_p_interp)  # [T_target, d_shared]

# Compute loss at boundary frames
loss = 0
for b in B:
    loss += ||z_c_proj[b] - z_p_proj[b]||^2

return loss / len(B)
